ill judge.","year":64},{"id":"recI9ahpTUBDhvXs8","ref":"Heb.13.5","text":"Let your conversation be without covetousness; and be content with such things as ye have: for he hath said, I will never leave thee, nor forsake thee.","year":64},{"id":"recReM6W9VNx4fz9F","ref":"Heb.13.6","text":"So that we may boldly say, The Lord is my helper, and I will not fear what man shall do unto me.","year":64},{"id":"recGiZ0773BXmx6rd","ref":"Heb.13.7","text":"Remember them which have the rule over you, who have spoken unto you the word of God: whose faith follow, considering the end of their conversation.","year":64},{"id":"rec5YHxogl0MtysHS","ref":"Heb.13.8","text":"Jesus Christ the same yesterday, and to day, and for ever.","year":64}]}
